In rugby union, Italy win their first match in the 2013 Six Nations Championship against tournament favourites France by a score of 23–18. (BBC) (RTÉ) (Al Jazeera)In boxing, 17-year-old Indonesian boxer Tubagus Sakti dies of a brain haemorrhage after losing a fight to Ical Tobida in Jakarta. (Boxing Scene) (Delfi Sport) (Bangkok Post)